---
title: "_getAssetPrice (Payment Abstraction V2)"
---
stateDiagram-v2
    direction TB
    [*] --> q_check_streams: check for fresh Streams price
    q_check_streams --> q_use_streams: streamsPrice exists AND not stale
    q_check_streams --> q_fallback: no fresh streams price

    q_use_streams --> q_validate: price = streamsPrice (scaled to feed decimals)
    q_fallback --> q_read_feed: read from usdDataFeed (Chainlink Data Feed)
    q_read_feed --> q_validate: price = dataFeedAnswer

    q_validate --> q_error: price == 0 OR price is stale
    q_error --> [*]: revert "invalid price"
    q_validate --> [*]: price > 0 AND not stale; return price

    note right of q_check_streams
        INV-031: Streams price takes priority over Data Feed price
        INV-032: fallback to Data Feed if Streams price is stale or missing
        INV-033: zero price always causes revert (never used in calculations)
        INV-034: staleness is checked against per-feed stalenessThreshold
    end note
